title: NFL playoffs, Patriots, Eagles, and being special
itunes:title: NFL playoffs, Patriots, Eagles, and being special
description:
Colin discusses the outcome of the NFL divisional playoff games, why this might be the best time to beat the New England Patriots, the Philadelphia Eagles overachieving, why the New Orleans Saints aren't as good as some think, and why the Dallas Cowboys are good, but not special. Guests include Terry Bradshaw, Matt Mosley, Jarrett Bell, Bucky Brooks, and Trent Dilfer.
